      "id": "piasnews-social-683fe67a8b6b5f36",
      "title": "X post from @laurogeitabat: yesterday: \"MV is in the final stage of negotiations to sign for mcl\" today: \"MV might end up i…",
      "title_zh": "X 发帖 @laurogeitabat：昨天：“MV 正处于与 MCL 签约的最后谈判阶段。”今天：“MV 有可能最终加入 MCL，但现在下定论还为时过早。”同一个人，24 小时之内说了完全相反的话。不管这些说法是真是假，F1 领域的新闻报道水平已经跌到了历史最低点。",
      "url": "https://x.com/laurogeitabat/status/2074777623981351233",
      "source": "@laurogeitabat",
      "source_handle": "laurogeitabat",
      "source_type": "x",
      "source_group": "fan_watch",
      "source_role": "fan_account",
