      "published_at_source": "platform_api_or_import",
      "date_verified": true,
      "discovered_at": "2026-07-10T12:25:37.309183Z",
      "category": "fan",
      "summary": "yesterday: \"MV is in the final stage of negotiations to sign for mcl\" today: \"MV might end up in mcl, but saying that right now is misleading\" same person, 24h apart. regardless of whether either, both, or none are true, the state of journalism in f1 is at an all time low",
